<img src="{{ logo }}" width="150" style="float:left;width:150px;margin:0 10px 10px 0;">

<p>Dear {{ participant.name }},</p>

{% if participant.fb_uid %}

  <p>You have successfully signed up with "<b>{{ group.name }}</b>" via Facebook. Welcome!</p>
  
  <p>To sign-in at any time with Facebook, go to the VoH home page at <a href="https://voh.intermix.org">https://voh.intermix.org</a> and click the Facebook icon. Or you can sign-in with your user-id and password:</p>

{% else %}

  {% if group.openness == 'open' %}

  <p>You have successfully signed up with "<b>{{ group.name }}</b>". Welcome!</p>

  <p>If you did not sign up for the group, simply ignore this email.</p>

  <p>Please confirm your sign-up by clicking the following link: {{ confirmlink }}. If the link doesn't work, copy and paste it into your browser window.</p>

  {% else %}

  <p>Please confirm your sign-up in InterMix by clicking the following link: {{ confirmlink }}. If the link doesn't work, copy and paste it into your browser window.</p>

  <p>After you have confirmed, the administrators of "<b>{{ group.name }}</b>" will need to approve your membership to the group. You'll be notified as soon as that happens.</p>

  <p>If you did not sign up for that group, simply ignore this email.</p>

  {% endif %}

  <p>Your user-id and password can be used to sign-in at <a href="https://{{ domain }}">{{ domain }}</a>. You must click the confirm link above before your password will work.</p>

{% endif %}

<p>User-ID: {{ participant.email }}<br>
Password: {{ password }}</p>

<p>If you have questions or comments, contact the system admin at <a href="mailto:questions@intermix.org">questions@intermix.org</a>.</p>

<p>Enjoy!</p>